entry.title: 1212 100% Authentic Colombian Push Up Jeans by B'Violet

Type: Bump Up Jeans
Price: 59.49

Made with a stretch denim/spandex fabric designed to comfortably give you the backside you desire.

Comfortable stretch cotton fabric.
Made in Colombia
